<view class="page {{hasRecommendations ? 'page-with-tray' : ''}}">
  <block wx:if="{{hasRecommendations}}">
    <view class="header">
      <view class="eyebrow">YOUR TOP 6</view>
      <view class="title">更值得你先了解的 6 个候选</view>
      <view class="lead">排序先考虑硬条件状态，再比较偏好匹配分。匹配分与证据等级是两个维度：高分不代表资料已被证实。</view>
      <view class="grade-note">
        <text class="grade">D</text>
        <text>当前资料以原型推断为主，只能支持“去核实”，不能支持“已确认适合”。</text>
      </view>
      <button class="edit-answer" bindtap="onEditAnswers">修改测评答案</button>
    </view>

    <view class="recommend-list">
      <view wx:for="{{recommendations}}" wx:key="club.id" class="recommend-item">
        <club-card
          club="{{item.club}}"
          rank="{{item.rank}}"
          score="{{item.score}}"
          evidence-grade="{{item.evidenceGrade}}"
          selected="{{item.selected}}"
          reasons="{{item.reasons}}"
          caution="{{item.caution}}"
          bindselect="onSelect"
          binddetail="onDetail"
        />
        <view class="decision-notes">
          <view class="note-row">
            <text class="note-label cost-label">代价</text>
            <text>{{item.costText}}</text>
          </view>
          <view class="note-row unknown-row">
            <text class="note-label unknown-label">未知</text>
            <text>{{item.unknownText}}</text>
          </view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </block>

  <view wx:else class="empty card">
    <view class="empty-title">还没有可展示的推荐</view>
    <view class="empty-copy">完成至少 8 题的专业测评后，这里会显示 Top 6、匹配理由、现实代价与未知项。</view>
    <button class="btn-primary" bindtap="onStartAssessment">开始测评</button>
  </view>
</view>

<selection-tray
  wx:if="{{hasRecommendations}}"
  clubs="{{selectedClubs}}"
  min="{{2}}"
  max="{{3}}"
  button-text="查看候选篮"
  bindremove="onRemove"
  bindcontinue="onOpenSelection"
/>
